htspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x5346+0+495/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F54%2F59%2Ff9a1b8be45b2b19fe814957e1af0%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-22.jpg" class="img" alt="The iconic lox bagel — a &amp;quot;Classic with the Works&amp;quot; — at Russ &amp;amp; Daughters." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 The iconic lox bagel — a "Classic with the Works" — at Russ &amp; Daughters.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Keren Carrion/NPR                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;New York's iconic Russ &amp; Daughters celebrates 100 years of slinging bagels and lox this year. Founded by Joel Russ, the shop, is one of the last remaining Jewish appetizing stores, which are distinct from delis. Unlike a traditional Jewish delicatessen, which serves smoked and cured meats like pastrami and corned beef, appetizing stores sell fresh fish and dairy. NPR's Scott Simon recently took a trip to the store to try his hand at the fine art of slicing salmon — a task that usually takes employees three months to learn. Read about the shop's rich history and new cookbook, &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/09/06/nx-s1-5382315/russ-daughters-niki-russ-federman-josh-russ-tupper" target="_blank"&gt;savor some delectable photos&lt;/a&gt;, and grab one of the new recipes. You're gonna want to eat a bagel afterward.&lt;/p&gt;       &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-87552" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 1756;         --source-height: 988;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1756x988+2+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd3%2F09%2Fa0db64764fdc87bbcc73a6b5979b%2Fnhpr-bear-brook-murders-jpg.jpg" class="img" alt="A headstone in an Allenstown cemetery honors two of the Bear Brook victims previously identified by New Hampshire investigators." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 A headstone in an Allenstown cemetery honors two of the Bear Brook victims previously identified by New Hampshire investigators.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Allie Gutierrez/NHPR file photo                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The New Hampshire Attorney General's office says it has identified the last unknown victim&lt;/strong&gt; in the high-profile cold case commonly known as the Bear Brook murders. Now, a &lt;a href="https://www.nhpr.org/nh-news/2025-09-07/bear-brook-murders-new-hampshire-cold-case-middle-child-mystery-terry-rasmussen-victim-identified" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;u&gt;new mystery emerges&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt; regarding the victim's missing mother. (via &lt;a href="https://www.nhpr.org/" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;u&gt;NHPR&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chrysler has recalled more than 90,000 Jeep Grand Cherokees &lt;/strong&gt;due to a software error that could lead to "&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/09/07/nx-s1-5533180/jeep-grand-cherokee-recall-plug-in-hybrid" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;u&gt;loss of drive power"&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and potential crashes, according to the U.S. National Highway Traffic Safety Administration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In 1980, 22-year-old Elaine Batchelor backpacked across Europe to celebrate her college graduation.&lt;/strong&gt; When two men tried to attack her one night on a train to Greece, two strangers stepped up to protect her. She says if she ever met her &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/09/08/nx-s1-5529374/alone-in-a-foreign-country-a-young-woman-is-saved-by-two-strangers" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;u&gt;unsung heroes&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt; again, she'd thank them for "doing what good humans do in moments like that."&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/g-s1-2467/obed-manuel"target="_blank"   &gt;&lt;em&gt;Obed Manuel.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
